    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> cpetig created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12315#discussion_r3447637235\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I thought about how to remove the duplication but this gets more difficult because one of the functions is const (this also makes the implementation less elegant as traits (and_then, try_from) don't work) and I didn't identify an obvious common dependency which is not core but component model specific.</p>\n<p>I think I addressed all other concerns.</p>\n</blockquote>",
